notes:
This record is for Approval for Access product AfA235. The Angling Guide database comprises approx 2000 records of private fisheries across England and Wales in 2011. Each of these private fisheries has public access, i.e. permits are available or club membership is available and there is no waiting list. 		
Each record includes:
• Location; 
• Contact information; 
• Information on the type of fishery.		
The Environment Agency stopped updating this dataset in 2011. Updated versions are available from the Angling Trust. Attribution statement: © Environment Agency copyright and/or database right 2015. All rights reserved.
